title: Basta
description: Vasily Vakulenko, known to the general public as the creator of several musical projects at once-Basta, Noggano and N1NTEND0, will perform his debut concert!

danceFloor.description: The dance floor, what else can we need to say :)

tableSeats.description: A comfortable place for four people. The price for a whole table.

title: Miyagi
description: As part of the European tour, Miyagi & Andy Panda will visit Warsaw for the first time with a big solo concert!

danceFloor.description: A huge dance floor is waiting for you, a bar is nearby :)

tableSeats.description: A comfortable place for four people. The possibility of ordering food/drinks. The price for a whole table.

title: SODA LUV
description: SODA LUV — a Russian artist, whom Morgenstern called the main hope of Russian rap, will perform in Lodz!

danceFloor.description: Don't drink too much, but if something happens,remeber, that the toilets are to the left of the stage :)

tableSeats.description: A comfortable place for four people. Calmer than on the dance floor :) The price for a whole table.

title: LIL KRYSTALLL
description: Lil Krystalll is a rapper from Riga, who became popular relatively recently. According to many people, the style of his music is very similar to such artists as Offi, OG Buda and Platinum.

danceFloor.description: One of the best dance floors in this galaxy.

tableSeats.description: The VIP table is waiting for your fifth points. The price for a whole table.

title: MAYOT
description: MAYOT is a young trap artist from Tyumen. He is a member of the creative association MELON MUSIC.Most recently, in September 2020, Artem released the next album called GHETTO GARDEN, after which he became really popular.

tableSeats.description: A little quieter, bar service, comfortable sofas. Price per table (for four)
